`is_altgr` may not fit macOS. The following code seems more clear.
```rust
    #[cfg(target_os = "macos")]
    // ignore right option key
    if event.code as u32 == rdev::kVK_RightOption {
        return events;
    }
    #[cfg(not(target_os = "macos"))]
    if is_altgr(event) {
        return events;
    }
```

